  "projectName": "NISIRA Assistant",
  "projectDescription": "A full-stack RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) conversational assistant that lets users ask questions against an internal document corpus, powered by a Django REST API backend, React SPA frontend, and a hybrid semantic + lexical retrieval pipeline with optional Google Drive document sync.",
