  "keyFeatures": [
    "Hybrid RAG pipeline combining 60% semantic (pgvector / ChromaDB) and 40% lexical search",
    "Adaptive top-k document retrieval (3–15 docs) based on query complexity",
    "Multi-provider LLM support: Gemini 2.0 Flash, OpenRouter, and Groq",
    "Google Drive document sync with automatic ingestion (PDF, DOCX, PPTX, XLSX, TXT)",
    "Conversational memory with LLM-based query reformulation",
    "Custom RAG evaluation metrics: Precision@k, Recall@k, Faithfulness, Hallucination Rate, WER",
    "JWT authentication with access/refresh token rotation",
    "React SPA with role-based routing (admin vs. regular user)",
    "React admin panel for document management, embeddings, and system metrics",
    "Dual vector store: PostgreSQL pgvector (production) and ChromaDB (local development)"
  ],
